For ActiveDirectory/Domain Controller, use:

	${RCD_SCRIPTS_DIR}/samba start

For traditional simple CIFS file sharing, use:

	${RCD_SCRIPTS_DIR}/nmbd start
	${RCD_SCRIPTS_DIR}/winbindd start
	${RCD_SCRIPTS_DIR}/smbd start
